            <l n="1">[{diš}]ARAD-gu10-ra u3-na-a-du11</l>
            <l n="2">⸢[{d}]šul⸣-gi lugal-zu na-ab-be2-a</l>
            <l n="3">[...]-⸢in⸣-ši-gi4-na-zu lu2-dun-a-zu#? in-nu</l>
            <l n="4">[...]-⸢zu⸣-ta a2 ag2-ga2 ⸢šu⸣ la-ba-ra-te-ge26-e</l>
            <l n="5">[a]-⸢na⸣-aš-am3 nig2 bi2-in-ak-a-ni ⸢ur5⸣ i3-mex(LA2)-a nu-zu</l>
            <l n="6">[...] ga2-gin7-nam ma-da gin6-ne2-de3</l>
            <l n="7">[...] x-de3 suhuš ma-da gi-en-gin6-ne2-de3</l>
            <l n="8">[...]-e-te-ge26-de3-na-zu umuš-bi zu-zu-am3</l>
            <l n="9">[...]-⸢ne⸣ inim-bi he2-en-zu</l>
