            <l n="11">[...] nam-ur-sag-ga2 [...]-⸢ra⸣ he2-en-šub-šub-bu</l>
            <l n="12">[...]-⸢ma⸣ he2-en-ri</l>
            <l n="13">[...]-⸢lib4⸣ a-ša3-ga u2-gu de2-ni-ib</l>
            <l n="14">[...] sa2-ne-en</l>
            <l n="15">[...]-ab igi-zu he2-in-ši-ku4</l>
            <l n="16">[...]-e#?-da-[...]-⸢ag2⸣</l>
            <l n="17">[...]-x</l>
          </div>
          <div n="reverse" type="textpart">
            <l n="1'">[...]-⸢ensi2⸣-[...] ⸢garza2⸣ nam-⸢garza2⸣-[...]</l>
            <l n="2'">[...]-⸢am3⸣ li-bi2-⸢ib⸣-[...]-ta-gub-bu</l>
            <l n="3'">[...] nu-un-hul</l>
            <l n="4'">[...]-ni#? lu2-lux(URU) al-diri-ge</l>
            <l n="5'">[...]-da ib2-gin6-ne</l>
            <l n="6'">[...]-mu-ag2</l>
            <l n="7'">[...] zu2#? keš2 ba-ra-na-ga2-ga2</l>
            <l n="8'">[...]-x aga-us2-zu nu-zu</l>
            <l n="9'">[...]-⸢lu⸣-ni u3 nam-ur-sag-ka-ni [...]-⸢zu⸣-u3 bi2-duh</l>
            <l n="10'">⸢tukumbi⸣ ama-a-tu-gu10 za-e-me-en</l>
            <l n="11'">[...]-ne-ne im sar-ra ⸢gu3⸣ he2-em-ta-de2-de2-e</l>
